        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "ss-ch-en-1-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The provider was operating across several branches, but supplier settlement logic was not equally disciplined everywhere. Payment cycles, deduction reasons, and approval timing varied too much from one branch to another.",
