          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "ss-ch-en-2",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "ss-ch-en-2-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That inconsistency created settlement delays, supplier disputes, and poor forecasting for finance teams. The business needed a branch-ready model that could standardize control without slowing the operation down.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
